{"componentChunkName":"component---node-modules-nehalist-gatsby-theme-nehalem-src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/2021-03-12-styled-material","result":{"data":{"post":{"id":"ec0f4cde-8780-590f-a8f3-cd1410aecd3a","headings":[{"depth":2},{"depth":2},{"depth":3},{"depth":2},{"depth":2}],"frontmatter":{"title":"[React] styled-component와 material-ui 사용하기","path":"/2021-03-12-styled-material","tags":["web","react"],"excerpt":"styled-component와 css 선택자에 대해 알아보자","created":"2021-03-12T00:00:00.000Z","createdPretty":"12 March, 2021","updated":"2021-03-12T00:00:00.000Z","updatedPretty":"12 March, 2021","featuredImage":{"childImageSharp":{"sizes":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.9047619047619047,"src":"/static/19f8023166c32c7bfa075fafc0f1ce31/f2cbb/styled-compoent-material-ui.jpg","srcSet":"/static/19f8023166c32c7bfa075fafc0f1ce31/8850c/styled-compoent-material-ui.jpg 200w,\n/static/19f8023166c32c7bfa075fafc0f1ce31/da113/styled-compoent-material-ui.jpg 400w,\n/static/19f8023166c32c7bfa075fafc0f1ce31/f2cbb/styled-compoent-material-ui.jpg 800w,\n/static/19f8023166c32c7bfa075fafc0f1ce31/c26c2/styled-compoent-material-ui.jpg 1200w,\n/static/19f8023166c32c7bfa075fafc0f1ce31/e3980/styled-compoent-material-ui.jpg 1504w","sizes":"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"}}}},"html":"<h2 id=\"들어가기-전에\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%93%A4%EC%96%B4%EA%B0%80%EA%B8%B0-%EC%A0%84%EC%97%90\" aria-label=\"들어가기 전에 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>[ 들어가기 전에 ]</h2>\n<p>이전 포스트에서 styled-component를 이용해 material-ui에 style을 줄 때 &#x26;&#x26;를 활용했다. 그게 어떤 원리로 적용되는지 한 번 살펴보고자 한다.<br>\n궁금한 분들은 <a href=\"https://goo-gy.github.io/2021-02-28-material-ui\">https://goo-gy.github.io/2021-02-28-material-ui</a>를 참고하길 바란다.  </p>\n<h2 id=\"css-선택자-우선순위\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#css-%EC%84%A0%ED%83%9D%EC%9E%90-%EC%9A%B0%EC%84%A0%EC%88%9C%EC%9C%84\" aria-label=\"css 선택자 우선순위 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>[ CSS 선택자 우선순위 ]</h2>\n<p>먼저 CSS가 적용되는 우선순위를 먼저 알아보자.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>!important를 붙인 속성</li>\n<li>html에서 직접 style을 지정</li>\n<li>id 선택자 (<strong>#id</strong>)</li>\n<li>class 선택자 (<strong>.class</strong>)</li>\n<li>태그 선택자</li>\n<li>상위 속성 상속</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"같은-우선순위인-경우\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B0%99%EC%9D%80-%EC%9A%B0%EC%84%A0%EC%88%9C%EC%9C%84%EC%9D%B8-%EA%B2%BD%EC%9A%B0\" aria-label=\"같은 우선순위인 경우 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>같은 우선순위인 경우?</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>부모-자식 관계가 많은 경우가 우선</li>\n<li>나중에 선언한 것이 우선</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"styled-components의-원리\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#styled-components%EC%9D%98-%EC%9B%90%EB%A6%AC\" aria-label=\"styled components의 원리 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>[ styled-components의 원리 ]</h2>\n<p>styled-component를 이용해 css를 입힌 예제를 살펴보자.</p>\n<iframe src=\"https://codesandbox.io/embed/styled-component-uk61d?fontsize=14&hidenavigation=1&theme=dark\"\n     style=\"width:100%; height:500px; border:0; border-radius: 4px; overflow:hidden;\"\n     title=\"styled-component\"\n     allow=\"accelerometer; ambient-light-sensor; camera; encrypted-media; geolocation; gyroscope; hid; microphone; midi; payment; usb; vr; xr-spatial-tracking\"\n     sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-modals allow-popups allow-presentation allow-same-origin allow-scripts\"\n></iframe>  \n예제에는 다음과 같은 3가지 element가 있다.  \n<ul>\n<li>아무런 style도 주지 않은 div  </li>\n<li>styled-components로 생성했지만 아무런 속성도 주지 않은 DivNone  </li>\n<li>styled-components로 css 속성을 준 DivBox  </li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 46.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"classSelector\"\n        title=\"classSelector\"\n        src=\"/static/d6dc208e70db91364679089d46e4adf4/e5166/classSelector.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d6dc208e70db91364679089d46e4adf4/f93b5/classSelector.jpg 300w,\n/static/d6dc208e70db91364679089d46e4adf4/b4294/classSelector.jpg 600w,\n/static/d6dc208e70db91364679089d46e4adf4/e5166/classSelector.jpg 1200w,\n/static/d6dc208e70db91364679089d46e4adf4/7e26b/classSelector.jpg 1510w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>  </p>\n<p>변환된 코드를 보면 styled-components는 class 선택자로 style을 생성하고 component에 해당하는 class를 전달하여 style을 적용하는 것을 알 수 있다.  </p>\n<h2 id=\"material-ui--styled-components\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#material-ui--styled-components\" aria-label=\"material ui  styled components permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>[ material-ui + styled-components ]</h2>\n<iframe src=\"https://codesandbox.io/embed/styled-components-w1x03?fontsize=14&hidenavigation=1&theme=dark\"\n     style=\"width:100%; height:500px; border:0; border-radius: 4px; overflow:hidden;\"\n     title=\"styled-components\"\n     allow=\"accelerometer; ambient-light-sensor; camera; encrypted-media; geolocation; gyroscope; hid; microphone; midi; payment; usb; vr; xr-spatial-tracking\"\n     sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-modals allow-popups allow-presentation allow-same-origin allow-scripts\"\n></iframe>  \nmaterial component에 styled-component로 그냥 style을 주면 제대로 적용되지 않지만, &&를 통해 style을 주니 적용되는 것을 확인할 수 있다.    \n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 34%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"doubleClass\"\n        title=\"doubleClass\"\n        src=\"/static/d4e8c0bdd6778a0a5f1b09d4efdc5815/e5166/doubleClass.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d4e8c0bdd6778a0a5f1b09d4efdc5815/f93b5/doubleClass.jpg 300w,\n/static/d4e8c0bdd6778a0a5f1b09d4efdc5815/b4294/doubleClass.jpg 600w,\n/static/d4e8c0bdd6778a0a5f1b09d4efdc5815/e5166/doubleClass.jpg 1200w,\n/static/d4e8c0bdd6778a0a5f1b09d4efdc5815/d9c39/doubleClass.jpg 1800w,\n/static/d4e8c0bdd6778a0a5f1b09d4efdc5815/0f98f/doubleClass.jpg 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span><br>\n해당 component의 css 부분을 보면 선택자로 .class가 두 번 중첩되어 있는 것을 확인할 수 있다.<br>\nmaterial-ui의 기본 디자인 역시 class 선택자로 style을 생성하고 class를 전달하는데,  </p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>우선순위가 같을 경우 부모-자식 관계가 많은 경우가 우선</strong>  </li>\n</ul>\n<p>이라는 규칙 때문에 material의 기본 style보다 &#x26;&#x26;으로 지정한 style이 더 우선적으로 적용되는 것 같다.  </p>\n<iframe height=\"265\" style=\"width: 100%;\" scrolling=\"no\" title=\"doubleClassName\" src=\"https://codepen.io/goo-gy/embed/jOVdpYR?height=265&theme-id=dark&default-tab=css,result\" frameborder=\"no\" loading=\"lazy\" allowtransparency=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\">\n  See the Pen <a href='https://codepen.io/goo-gy/pen/jOVdpYR'>doubleClassName</a> by Googy\n  (<a href='https://codepen.io/goo-gy'>@goo-gy</a>) on <a href='https://codepen.io'>CodePen</a>.\n</iframe>  \n이해를 돕기 위해서 비슷한 예제를 가져왔다.  "},"primaryTag":null},"pageContext":{"postId":"ec0f4cde-8780-590f-a8f3-cd1410aecd3a","primaryTag":"web"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1116962356","1994268275","2206391224","2275848304","545095672"]}